\begin_inset Formula $X_{1},...,X_{k}$
\end_inset

 are independent, if 
\begin_inset Formula $X_{i}$
\end_inset

 has the normal distribution with mean 
\begin_inset Formula $\mu_{i}$
\end_inset

 and variance 
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma_{i}^{2}$
\end_inset

 
\begin_inset Formula $(i=1,...,k)$
